.SH Name
.SP 5 5
exit_move -  This is the main code for moving someone.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int exit_move(string verb,
string extra,
string special,
object thing)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^verb%^RESET%^ - the movement verb
%^BOLD%^extra%^RESET%^ - extra information
%^BOLD%^special%^RESET%^ - special information
%^BOLD%^thing%^RESET%^ - the thing to move
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/room_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is the main code for moving someone.  The move_thing code above
should not be called directly.  This code handlers all the followers
and any other things that need to be handled.
.EP

